@startuml 自动化控制模块用例图

left to right direction

actor "学校管理员" as Admin
actor "系统" as System

usecase "创建自动化规则" as UC1
usecase "查询自动化规则列表" as UC2
usecase "启用/禁用规则" as UC3
usecase "删除自动化规则" as UC4
usecase "自动化控制执行" as UC5
usecase "下发控制指令" as UC6
usecase "查询控制指令历史" as UC7

Admin --> UC1
Admin --> UC2
Admin --> UC3
Admin --> UC4
Admin --> UC6
Admin --> UC7
System --> UC5

UC1 .> UC2 : <<include>>
UC5 .> UC6 : <<include>>
UC5 .> UC7 : <<include>>

note right of UC5
  系统根据规则条件自动
  检测并执行控制动作
end note

@enduml